---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import OperationFlow from '../components/OperationFlow.astro';
import LiveDemo from '../components/LiveDemo.astro';
import FAQ from '../components/FAQ.astro';
const chat = 'https://chat.neoflowoff.agency';
const benefits = [['Menos oportunidades perdidas','Leads são atendidos antes que o interesse desapareça.'],['Mais contexto para o comercial','A equipe recebe nome, contato, origem, necessidade e histórico da conversa.'],['Dados conectados à aquisição','Origem, eventos e conversões continuam sendo registrados.']];
const infra = ['Página','Agente SDR','Captura','Dados','CRM','Handoff humano','Meta CAPI'];
const offer = ['Diagnóstico inicial da jornada','Configuração do Agente SDR','Adaptação de linguagem e oferta','Página ou superfície de atendimento','Captura e persistência de leads','Identificação de origem','Integração de handoff','Pixel e Meta CAPI','Acompanhamento inicial'];
---
<Layout title="Operação SDR IA Plug & Play | neoflowoff.agency" description="Agente SDR, página, captura de leads, qualificação, handoff humano e Meta CAPI conectados em uma operação comercial implantada pela neoflowoff.agency.">
  <div class="page-shell"><Header /><main><Hero />
    <section class="section problem"><span class="kicker">01 / O PROBLEMA REAL</span><div class="problem-grid"><h2>O lead chegou.<br /><em>A operação é que não estava pronta para recebê-lo.</em></h2><div class="scene reveal"><p>A campanha gera uma mensagem.<br />A pessoa pergunta preço.<br />Alguém demora para responder.</p><p>Quando o comercial assume, já não sabe de onde ela veio, qual anúncio iniciou a conversa ou o que ela realmente queria.</p><strong>O problema não é apenas gerar leads. É conseguir agir enquanto ainda existe intenção.</strong></div></div></section>
    <OperationFlow />
    <section class="section benefits"><div class="section-head"><span class="kicker">03 / IMPACTO</span><h2>O comercial deixa de<br /><em>começar do zero.</em></h2></div><div class="benefit-grid">{benefits.map(([title,copy],i)=><article class="reveal"><span>0{i+1}</span><h3>{title}</h3><p>{copy}</p></article>)}</div></section>
    <LiveDemo />
    <section class="section infrastructure" id="infraestrutura"><div class="section-head"><span class="kicker">05 / INFRAESTRUTURA</span><h2>A conversa é apenas a superfície.<br /><em>O valor está no que acontece depois dela.</em></h2></div><div class="infra-line">{infra.map((item,i)=><div class="infra-node reveal"><span>0{i+1}</span><b>{item}</b></div>)}</div><div class="infra-bottom"><p>Página e chat · identificação de origem · captura de contato · persistência de dados · lifecycle comercial · handoff humano · Pixel e Meta CAPI · APIs e webhooks.</p><strong>O agente conversa. A infraestrutura organiza o que essa conversa gera.</strong></div></section>
    <section class="section offer" id="oferta"><div class="offer-copy"><span class="kicker">06 / A OFERTA</span><h2>Operação SDR IA<br /><em>Plug & Play.</em></h2><p>Implantamos uma operação preparada para receber, qualificar e encaminhar oportunidades dentro do fluxo comercial da empresa.</p><div class="concierge">CONCIERGE <span>Configuração conduzida diretamente pela neoflowoff.agency, sem painéis complexos ou onboarding self-service.</span></div><a class="button" href={chat}>Avaliar minha operação <span>↗</span></a></div><ul>{offer.map((item,i)=><li class="reveal"><span>0{i+1}</span>{item}<i>✓</i></li>)}</ul></section>
    <section class="section proof"><span class="kicker">07 / PROVA OPERACIONAL</span><div class="proof-grid"><h2>A demonstração não é um vídeo.<br /><em>É a própria operação.</em></h2><div><p>O mesmo sistema utilizado para receber esta conversa faz parte da infraestrutura aplicada pela neoflowoff.agency em páginas, agentes, dados e fluxos comerciais.</p><div class="proof-tags">{['Operação em produção','Agente SDR real','Infraestrutura conectada','Dados e eventos','Integração com Meta','Automação e handoff'].map(x=><span>{x}</span>)}</div></div></div></section>
    <FAQ />
    <section class="section final-cta"><div class="final-signal"><i></i><span>OPERAÇÃO PRONTA PARA RECEBER SINAL</span></div><h2>Se o lead chegou, ele já custou<br /><em>atenção, tempo ou dinheiro.</em></h2><p>Agora precisamos garantir que a operação faça alguma coisa com ele.</p><a class="button" href={chat}>Iniciar diagnóstico <span>↗</span></a><small>Converse com o NΞØ:One e mostre como os leads chegam hoje na sua empresa.</small></section>
  </main><footer><a class="brand" href="#top">NEØ<span>FLOWOFF</span><small>.agency</small></a><p>Agentes de IA, páginas, CRM e fluxos comerciais para empresas.<br />Marketing com infraestrutura.</p><div><a href="https://www.instagram.com/neoflw.agency">Instagram</a><a href="https://linkedin.com/company/neoflw-agency">LinkedIn</a><a href={chat}>Contato</a><a href={chat}>Conversar com o NΞØ:One</a></div><small>© {new Date().getFullYear()} neoflowoff.agency</small></footer></div>
  <a class="chat-bubble" href={chat} aria-label="Conversar com o NΞØ:One"><i></i><span>NΞØ:One<small>Iniciar diagnóstico</small></span><b>↗</b></a>
  <script>const observer=new IntersectionObserver(es=>es.forEach(e=>{if(e.isIntersecting)e.target.classList.add('visible')}),{threshold:.12});document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(e=>observer.observe(e));</script>
</Layout>
<style is:global>
:root{--acid:#8ffe09;--cyan:#5ae7e7;--bg:#080908;--panel:#101210;--line:#282b27;--text:#f0f2ed;--muted:#92978f}*{box-sizing:border-box}html{scroll-behavior:smooth}body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:Geist,Arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.5}body:before{content:"";position:fixed;inset:0;pointer-events:none;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.018) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,.018) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:64px 64px;mask-image:linear-gradient(to bottom,black,transparent 70%)}a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}.page-shell{max-width:1440px;margin:auto;border-left:1px solid #171917;border-right:1px solid #171917}.header{height:78px;display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 5vw;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);position:sticky;top:0;background:rgba(8,9,8,.88);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);z-index:20}.brand{font:600 18px/1 Space Grotesk;letter-spacing:-.8px}.brand span{color:var(--acid)}.brand small{font:400 11px Geist;color:var(--muted);margin-left:3px}.header nav{display:flex;gap:30px;margin:auto;font-size:13px;color:#aeb3ab}.header nav a:hover{color:var(--acid)}.button{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:30px;min-height:54px;padding:0 22px;background:var(--acid);color:#071002;font-weight:650;font-size:14px;clip-path:polygon(0 0,calc(100% - 12px) 0,100% 12px,100% 100%,12px 100%,0 calc(100% - 12px));transition:.2s}.button:hover{filter:brightness(1.12);transform:translateY(-2px)}.button-small{min-height:40px;padding:0 16px;gap:18px;font-size:12px}.section{padding:120px 7vw;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);position:relative}.hero{min-height:730px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.15fr .85fr;gap:7vw;align-items:center;padding-top:100px}.eyebrow,.kicker{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;font-weight:600;color:var(--muted)}.eyebrow i,.final-signal i,.agent-id i{display:inline-block;width:7px;height:7px;background:var(--acid);border-radius:50%;box-shadow:0 0 12px var(--acid);margin-right:8px}.hero h1,.section h2{font-family:Space Grotesk,sans-serif;letter-spacing:-.055em;line-height:.96;margin:28px 0;font-weight:500}.hero h1{font-size:clamp(50px,5.4vw,82px)}h1 span,h2 em{color:var(--acid);font-style:normal}.lead{max-width:690px;font-size:19px;color:#d5d9d1}.support{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted)}.actions{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:30px;margin-top:36px}.text-link{font-size:13px;border-bottom:1px solid #50544e;padding:15px 0}.signal-panel{background:linear-gradient(145deg,#11140f,#0b0d0b);border:1px solid #33392e;box-shadow:0 30px 90px #000;padding:22px;position:relative}.panel-top,.panel-bottom{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.16em;color:#6f766d}.panel-top i{display:inline-block;width:5px;height:5px;background:var(--acid);border-radius:50%;margin-right:5px}.signal-core{height:190px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;position:relative;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}.signal-core span{font:600 28px Space Grotesk;z-index:2}.signal-core small{color:var(--muted);z-index:2}.pulse{position:absolute;width:120px;height:120px;border:1px solid #426e1c;border-radius:50%;box-shadow:0 0 50px #8ffe0915,inset 0 0 50px #8ffe0915}.signal-panel ol{list-style:none;margin:0;padding:12px 0}.signal-panel li,.offer li{display:grid;grid-template-columns:40px 1fr 20px;padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #232620;align-items:center}.signal-panel li span,.offer li span{color:#62685f;font:10px Space Grotesk}.signal-panel li b{font-size:12px}.signal-panel li i,.offer li i{color:var(--acid);font-style:normal}.panel-bottom{padding-top:14px;justify-content:center}.section-head{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;gap:50px}.section h2{font-size:clamp(40px,4.8vw,69px)}.section-head .kicker{padding-top:15px}.problem-grid,.proof-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.15fr .85fr;gap:8vw}.scene{padding-top:30px}.scene p{font-size:18px;color:#b7bcb4;margin:0 0 26px}.scene strong{display:block;border-left:2px solid var(--acid);padding-left:20px;font-size:16px}.flow-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);margin-top:70px;border-top:1px solid var(--line);border-left:1px solid var(--line)}.flow-card{padding:28px;min-height:250px;border-right:1px solid var(--line);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);background:#0b0c0b}.flow-card>div{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;color:#666b64;font-size:11px}.flow-card>div i{width:7px;height:7px;border:1px solid var(--acid);border-radius:50%}.flow-card h3,.benefit-grid h3{font:500 26px Space Grotesk;margin:55px 0 14px}.flow-card p,.benefit-grid p,.demo p,.offer p,.proof p{color:var(--muted)}.benefit-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:18px;margin-top:70px}.benefit-grid article{padding:30px;background:var(--panel);border-top:1px solid #394033}.benefit-grid span{color:var(--acid);font-size:10px}.demo{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8vw;background:radial-gradient(circle at 80% 50%,#8ffe0910,transparent 32%)}.demo-action{border:1px solid #343a30;background:#0e100e;padding:35px}.agent-id{display:flex;gap:18px;align-items:center;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);padding-bottom:25px}.agent-mark{width:64px;height:64px;border:1px solid var(--acid);display:grid;place-items:center;font:600 17px Space Grotesk;color:var(--acid)}.agent-id strong{display:block;font:600 20px Space Grotesk}.agent-id span{display:block;color:var(--acid);font-size:9px;margin-top:6px}.demo-action p{margin:30px 0}.button-wide{width:100%}.demo-action>small,.final-cta>small{display:block;color:#6f756c;font-size:11px;margin-top:15px;text-align:center}.infra-line{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(7,1fr);margin:70px 0;position:relative}.infra-line:before{content:"";height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--acid),var(--cyan));position:absolute;top:17px;left:3%;right:3%}.infra-node{position:relative;text-align:center}.infra-node span{margin:auto;display:grid;place-items:center;width:35px;height:35px;background:#0b0d0a;border:1px solid var(--acid);border-radius:50%;font-size:9px;color:var(--acid);position:relative}.infra-node b{display:block;margin-top:15px;font-size:12px}.infra-bottom{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:10vw;border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding-top:30px}.infra-bottom p{max-width:680px;color:var(--muted);font-size:13px}.infra-bottom strong{max-width:350px}.offer{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8vw}.concierge{display:flex;gap:20px;color:var(--acid);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.1em;border:1px solid #3e5130;padding:18px;margin:30px 0}.concierge span{color:#a8ada5;letter-spacing:0;font-size:12px}.offer ul{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0}.offer li{grid-template-columns:45px 1fr 20px;padding:16px 0;font-size:14px}.proof{background:#0d0f0d}.proof-tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;margin-top:35px}.proof-tags span{border:1px solid #353a33;padding:9px 12px;font-size:11px;color:#b3b8b0}.faq-list{margin-top:60px;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}details{border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}summary{cursor:pointer;list-style:none;display:grid;grid-template-columns:60px 1fr 30px;padding:24px 0;font:500 18px Space Grotesk}summary span{font:10px Geist;color:#62675f;padding-top:6px}summary i{color:var(--acid);font-style:normal;font-size:22px;transition:.2s}details[open] summary i{transform:rotate(45deg)}details p{margin:0 60px 25px;max-width:700px;color:var(--muted)}.final-cta{text-align:center;padding-top:140px;padding-bottom:140px;background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 60%,#8ffe0910,transparent 35%)}.final-signal{color:var(--muted);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.18em}.final-cta p{color:var(--muted);font-size:17px}.final-cta .button{margin-top:25px}footer{padding:60px 7vw;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 2fr 2fr auto;gap:35px;align-items:start}footer p{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin:0}footer>div{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:18px;font-size:11px}footer>small{color:#5d625a;font-size:9px}.chat-bubble{position:fixed;right:24px;bottom:24px;background:#121511;border:1px solid #3f4d36;padding:12px 14px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;z-index:30;box-shadow:0 15px 40px #000}.chat-bubble>i{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--acid);box-shadow:0 0 10px var(--acid)}.chat-bubble span{font:600 12px Space Grotesk}.chat-bubble small{display:block;font:400 9px Geist;color:var(--muted)}.chat-bubble b{color:var(--acid)}.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px);transition:.65s ease}.reveal.visible{opacity:1;transform:none}@media(max-width:900px){.header{padding:0 20px}.header nav{display:none}.header .button{margin-left:auto}.section{padding:80px 24px}.hero{grid-template-columns:1fr;min-height:auto;padding-top:70px}.hero h1{font-size:49px}.signal-panel{margin-top:25px}.problem-grid,.proof-grid,.demo,.offer{grid-template-columns:1fr}.section-head{display:block}.flow-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.benefit-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.infra-line{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px}.infra-line:before{display:none}.infra-node{display:flex;align-items:center;text-align:left;border:1px solid var(--line);padding:10px}.infra-node span{margin:0 12px 0 0}.infra-node b{margin:0}.infra-bottom{display:block}.offer ul{margin-top:30px}footer{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.chat-bubble span{display:none}}@media(max-width:560px){.header{height:68px}.header .button{font-size:0;width:42px;padding:0}.header .button span{font-size:15px}.hero{padding-top:55px}.hero h1{font-size:43px}.lead{font-size:16px}.actions{align-items:stretch;flex-direction:column;gap:8px}.text-link{text-align:center}.section h2{font-size:39px}.flow-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.flow-card{min-height:210px}.demo-action{padding:22px}.infra-line{grid-template-columns:1fr}.concierge{flex-direction:column}.problem-grid{gap:5px}summary{grid-template-columns:35px 1fr 25px;font-size:16px}details p{margin-left:35px}.final-cta{padding:100px 22px}footer{grid-template-columns:1fr}.chat-bubble{right:14px;bottom:14px}.proof-grid{gap:12px}}
</style>
